ciphers, including MMB, Square,

27
00:01:58,033 --> 00:02:01,299
SHARK, NOEKEON,
3-Way and BaseKing.

28
00:02:01,366 --> 00:02:05,633
In the late 90s, he co-designed
with Vincent Rijmen, the

29
00:02:05,700 --> 00:02:09,265
