also a Belgian cryptographer
and a graduate of KU Leuven.

47
00:02:58,733 --> 00:03:02,466
He is, obviously, the
co-designer of Rijndael cipher,

48
00:03:02,533 --> 00:03:04,266
now the Advanced
Encryption Standard.

