51
00:03:11,333 --> 00:03:12,566
NOEKEON and SHARK.

52
00:03:13,699 --> 00:03:17,333
Vincent has had a career in both
industry and academia and is

53
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:19,733
currently a professor
in KU Leuven Belgium.

54
00:03:20,833 --> 00:03:23,533
In 2019, he became a fellow at
the International Association

55
00:03:23,599 --> 00:03:26,632
for Cryptologic Research for
his well-known contributions

56
00:03:26,699 --> 00:03:28,666
to cryptography.

57
00:03:28,733 --> 00:03:32,933
The Advanced Encryption Standard
or AES which is the joint design

58
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:37,000
of Professors Daemen and Rijmen
is now used everywhere for

59
00:03:37,066 --> 00:03:38,466
data encryption.

60
00:03:38,533 --> 00:03:41,732
It serves as an amazing example
of the power of mathematical

61
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:44,833
cryptography to influence
and secure our world.

62
00:03:45,533 --> 00:03:49,833
For these contributions and many
more, we hereby award Professor

63
00:03:49,900 --> 00:03:54,599
Joan Daemen and Professor
Vincent Rijmen the RSA 2020

64
00:03:54,666 --> 00:03:57,433
Conference Award for Excellence
in the Field of Mathematics.

65
